@aljoscha Sorry, you are right. There is still a problem here.
In fact the return map of `AppliedPTransform.getOutputs()`is an `ImmutableMap`, its implementation is `RegularImmutableMap`, its entrySet order is the same with the order of insertion.
We should use the original `AppliedPTransform.getOutputs()` to produce labels instead of the newly generated HashMap (`Map<TupleTag<?>, OutputTag<WindowedValue<?>>> mapping`).
